"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-adrian-wildschutt-sets-south-africa-record-in-10-000m-final-breakiing-result\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.8849520962629741, \"rank\": 0.1274964477765334, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbAdrian Wildschutt sets South Africa record in 10 000m final  Adrian Wildschutt set an eye-catching South African record in the men's 10 000m final at the Paris Olympics 2024 on Friday.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.8849520962629741, \"rank\": 0.1274964477765334, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999995150020634, \"rank\": 4.847787634806938e-07, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adrian Wildschuttcontinued his rise up ladder of elite track distance runners, with an eye-catching South African record of 26:50.64 in the men's 10 000m final at the Paris Olympics 2024 on Friday.\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy the Paris Olympic Games 2024 experience at your favourite ATKV Resort!\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ATKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the swimming programme coming to an end, the main focus switched to the Stade de France stadium which is playing host to track and field for the next week.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 744, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Day one finished with the lights on as Wildschutt left everything out on the track and after 25 laps of an energy-sapping fast race, he had a bright NR next to his name.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The gold medal was won by Uganda'sJoshua Cheptegeiin an Olympic record 27:24.25, having sprinted clear of the opposition down the straight for the final time.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Seven Africans filled the first 10 places, with Adrian Wildschutt only fading late to 10th place overall.\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He had matched strides with the main pack for long periods of the race and he was still right in contention after 7 000m, in fact, occupying fourth spot in 18.46.1.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He even felt it was only in the last lap that things got away with him.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought I ran really smart,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew I'd have to be really good in the last three, four laps.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I moved up and got myself in an amazing position.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I stuck with the pack and it was only in the last 300m that I started struggling, I am very satisfied and very grateful for everything that I have been able to accomplish so far.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My coach an I discussed things and the plan was to conserve as much energy as possible, know I'd have to run a fast last 1 000m.\\\"\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section for free-to-read content  WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2094, \"end\": 2097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999999770420802, \"rank\": 1.6986331732092535e-08, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 2098, \"end\": 2100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.9992486330833631, \"rank\": 0.0007508619319748362, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on Facebook for the latest local and international news  Follow The South African's WhatsApp channel for the latest sport, lifestyle and local news  Follow The South African on X for the latest, breaking news  A brand new shopping mall is coming to Pretoria East, bringing major retailers and new convenience to the area.\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2322, \"end\": 2330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9999372766109925, \"rank\": 6.272732336235203e-05, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orlando Pirates are reportedly set to welcome a new staff member in former Stellenbosch FC Head of Recruitment Brendon Fourie.\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2569, \"end\": 2576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pittsburgh_Pirates\", \"score\": 0.8338310410489757, \"rank\": 0.19928162954740478, \"text\": \"Pirates\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pittsburgh_Pirates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pittsburgh_Pirates\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Masindi Nemtajela was stretched off during Orlando Pirates' 6-0 win over TS Galaxy on Sunday afternoon in Mbombela.\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2689, \"end\": 2696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masindi\", \"score\": 0.9991696228971515, \"rank\": 0.0008310672019210369, \"text\": \"Masindi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masindi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masindi\"}, {\"begin\": 2762, \"end\": 2771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TS_Galaxy_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TS Galaxy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TS_Galaxy_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TS_Galaxy_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 2795, \"end\": 2803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mbombela\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2870084762668495e-17, \"text\": \"Mbombela\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \